"\">keyboard shortcut</link>, or a <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">menubar</link> option."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
